summary: El deber, el honor antes que la felicidad
title: El deber, el honor antes que la felicidad
description:
by 0Aressama1

“-si llegará un día en que tú padre tuviera que elegir entre su honor, por un lado, y sus seres amados por otro, ¿qué haría? –” Su padre haría lo que era correcto, incluso si eso significaba sacrificar a la felicidad de su familia.

Ante las injusticias que enfrenta el reino, el abandono del pueblo, la indiferencia de los Lores y Nobles del Reino ante la decadencia, Eddard «Ned» Stark, decide jugar el Juego de Tronos, después de todo tiene su propio candidato al trono quien lleva su sangre y decide hacer las paces con viejos enemigos por el bien del reino.

Podrá llegar hasta el final mientras intentar crear un equilibrio entre su honor, su deber y sus deseos de proteger a su familia, o serán sus deseos de proteger a todo el reino quien le hagan perder lo todo.

summary: I had a Jonsa wedding dream last night, that after Jon’s parentage was revealed, the northern lords demanded Jon and Sansa marry...
body:
I had a Jonsa wedding dream last night, that after Jon’s parentage was revealed, the northern lords demanded Jon and Sansa marry to tie the inheritance back to the Starks and away from the Targs.

And Jon and Sansa were awkward but agreed but Arya demanded that all the lords, ladies and heirs swear blood oaths on the weirwood tree before the wedding could begin, and that they send a heap of second sons to form king and queen guards.

This was intended to ensure that if anything went badly (a long winter or crops failing or no heirs) the northern lords couldn’t bitch that the old gods disapproved because Jon and Sansa were raised as siblings.

Arya’s thinking was that all who had put blood into the tree had not only shown their support but that somehow Bran would know if they had rebellious thoughts in the future?

Arya wore a white wool dress as Sansa’s bridesmaid but it was covered in blood spray by the time Sansa came down. Sansa liked the blood pattern so much she had it added to her Queensguard uniforms.
